Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Class LitmusAssertionsBaseVisitor<T>

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen.LitmusAssertionsBaseVisitor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
LitmusAssertionsVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
public class LitmusAssertionsBaseVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T> implements LitmusAssertionsVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of LitmusAssertionsVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
